            </div>
            <div class="logo-cell">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"
                ><path
                  d="M22.2819 9.8211a5.9847 5.9847 0 0 0-.5157-4.9108 6.0462 6.0462 0 0 0-6.5098-2.9A6.0651 6.0651 0 0 0 4.9807 4.1818a5.9847 5.9847 0 0 0-3.9977 2.9 6.0462 6.0462 0 0 0 .7427 7.0966 5.98 5.98 0 0 0 .511 4.9107 6.051 6.051 0 0 0 6.5146 2.9001A5.9847 5.9847 0 0 0 13.2599 24a6.0557 6.0557 0 0 0 5.7718-4.2058 5.9894 5.9894 0 0 0 3.9977-2.9001 6.0557 6.0557 0 0 0-.7475-7.0729zm-9.022 12.6081a4.4755 4.4755 0 0 1-2.8764-1.0408l.1419-.0804 4.7783-2.7582a.7948.7948 0 0 0 .3927-.6813v-6.7369l2.02 1.1686a.071.071 0 0 1 .038.052v5.5826a4.504 4.504 0 0 1-4.4945 4.4944zm-9.6607-4.1254a4.4708 4.4708 0 0 1-.5346-3.0137l.142.0852 4.783 2.7582a.7712.7712 0 0 0 .7806 0l5.8428-3.3685v2.3324a.0804.0804 0 0 1-.0332.0615L9.74 19.9502a4.4992 4.4992 0 0 1-6.1408-1.6464zM2.3408 7.8956a4.485 4.485 0 0 1 2.3655-1.9728V11.6a.7664.7664 0 0 0 .3879.6765l5.8144 3.3543-2.0201 1.1685a.0757.0757 0 0 1-.071 0l-4.8303-2.7865A4.504 4.504 0 0 1 2.3408 7.872zm16.5963 3.8558L13.1038 8.364 15.1192 7.2a.0757.0757 0 0 1 .071 0l4.8303 2.7913a4.4944 4.4944 0 0 1-.6765 8.1042v-5.6772a.79.79 0 0 0-.407-.667zm2.0107-3.0231l-.142-.0852-4.7735-2.7818a.7759.7759 0 0 0-.7854 0L9.409 9.2297V6.8974a.0662.0662 0 0 1 .0284-.0615l4.8303-2.7866a4.4992 4.4992 0 0 1 6.6802 4.66zM8.3065 12.863l-2.02-1.1638a.0804.0804 0 0 1-.038-.0567V6.0742a4.4992 4.4992 0 0 1 7.3757-3.4537l-.142.0805L8.704 5.459a.7948.7948 0 0 0-.3927.6813zm1.0976-2.3654l2.602-1.4998 2.6069 1.4998v2.9994l-2.5974 1.4997-2.6067-1.4997Z"
                ></path></svg
              >
              <span class="logo-name">Codex</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-cell">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"
                ><path
                  d="M12 0C5.37 0 0 5.37 0 12c0 5.31 3.435 9.795 8.205 11.385.6.105.825-.255.825-.57 0-.285-.015-1.23-.015-2.235-3.015.555-3.795-.735-4.035-1.41-.135-.345-.72-1.41-1.23-1.695-.42-.225-1.02-.78-.015-.795.945-.015 1.62.87 1.845 1.23 1.08 1.815 2.805 1.305 3.495.99.105-.78.42-1.305.765-1.605-2.67-.3-5.46-1.335-5.46-5.925 0-1.305.465-2.385 1.23-3.225-.12-.3-.54-1.53.12-3.18 0 0 1.005-.315 3.3 1.23.96-.27 1.98-.405 3-.405s2.04.135 3 .405c2.295-1.56 3.3-1.23 3.3-1.23.66 1.65.24 2.88.12 3.18.765.84 1.23 1.905 1.23 3.225 0 4.605-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.925.435.375.81 1.095.81 2.22 0 1.605-.015 2.895-.015 3.3 0 .315.225.69.825.57A12.02 12.02 0 0024 12c0-6.63-5.37-12-12-12z"
                ></path></svg
              >
              <span class="logo-name">GitHub Copilot</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-cell">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                ><polyline points="4 17 10 11 4 5"></polyline><line
                  x1="12"
                  y1="19"
                  x2="20"
                  y2="19"></line></svg
              >
              <span class="logo-name">Executor CLI</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-cell">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                ><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"></circle><path
                  d="M3.5 9h17M3.5 15h17M12 3a14 14 0 0 1 0 18M12 3a14 14 0 0 0 0 18"
                ></path></svg
              >
              <span class="logo-name">Any MCP client</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-4 gap-y-3 mt-8">
            <span class="badge-chip">MCP</span>
            <span class="badge-sep"></span>
            <span class="badge-chip">OpenAPI</span>
            <span class="badge-sep"></span>
            <span class="badge-chip">GraphQL</span>
            <span class="badge-sep"></span>
            <span class="badge-chip">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                ><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg
              >Open source, MIT
            </span>
            <span class="badge-sep"></span>
            <span class="badge-chip">Self-host or cloud</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      {/* ─── WEDGE ─── */}
      <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 border-t border-rule">
        <div class="reveal max-w-[840px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-10">
          <p
            class="text-[clamp(1.5rem,3.4vw,2.2rem)] font-medium tracking-[-0.02em] leading-[1.28] text-ink text-balance"
          >
            Wiring tools to agents is fiddly, per-client, and easy to get wrong.
            Executor makes every tool, from any protocol, look the
            <span class="serif-italic">same</span>: one name, one input
            schema, one output schema, so any agent can call any of them
            the same way.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      {/* ─── NO CONTEXT BLOAT (interactive) ─── */}
      <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 border-t border-rule">
        <div class="reveal max-w-[1100px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-10">
          <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
            <div class="eyebrow mb-4">Context efficiency</div>
            <h2 class="section-title mx-auto max-w-[20ch] mb-5">
              Thousands of tools, no <span class="serif-italic">bloat</span>.
            </h2>
            <p class="section-sub mx-auto max-w-[58ch]">
              Connect everything you use and Executor still shows the model a
              single tool. It searches your catalog and loads a tool's schema
              only when the code actually calls it, so the prompt never
              balloons.
            </p>
          </div>

          <ContextBloatDemo client:load />
        </div>
      </section>

      {/* ─── CAPABILITIES ─── */}
      <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 border-t border-rule">
        <div class="reveal max-w-[1100px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-10">
          <div class="mb-12 max-w-[34ch]">
            <div class="eyebrow mb-4">What you get</div>
            <h2 class="section-title">
              The model reasons. Executor handles the
              <span class="serif-italic">rest</span>.
            </h2>
          </div>

          <div class="cap-grid">
            {/* One tool shape */}
            <div class="cap-card">
              <span class="cap-icon"
                ><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                  ><path d="m12 2 9 5-9 5-9-5 9-5Z"></path><path
                    d="m3 12 9 5 9-5"></path><path d="m3 17 9 5 9-5"
                  ></path></svg
                ></span
              >
              <h3>One tool shape</h3>
              <p>
                MCP, OpenAPI, GraphQL, or a custom integration. Under the hood
                they all become a tool name, an input schema, and an output
                schema.
              </p>
            </div>

            {/* Code-mode */}
            <div class="cap-card">
              <span class="cap-icon"
                ><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                  ><polyline points="4 17 10 11 4 5"></polyline><line
                    x1="12"
                    y1="19"
                    x2="20"
                    y2="19"></line></svg
                ></span
              >
              <h3>Call it any way</h3>
              <p>
                Today it is a code-mode MCP. It could just as well be the
                Executor CLI, a one-off script, a gen-UI dashboard, or a reusable
                workflow. Same tools, every surface.
              </p>
            </div>

            {/* Trace every call */}
            <div class="cap-card">
              <span class="cap-icon"
                ><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                  ><path d="M3 12h4l3 8 4-16 3 8h4"></path></svg
                ></span
              >
              <h3>Trace every call</h3>
              <p class="mb-1">
                One place to see every run and tool call. Audit any
                decision after the fact.
              </p>
              <div class="cap-visual trace">
                <div class="trace-row is-root">
                  <span class="lbl">run_7421</span>
                  <span class="track"
                    ><span class="bar" style="left:0%;width:100%"></span></span
                  >
                  <span class="dur">1.42s</span>
                </div>
                <div class="trace-row">
                  <span class="lbl">sentry.getIssue</span>
                  <span class="track"
                    ><span class="bar" style="left:0%;width:18%"></span></span
                  >
                  <span class="dur">184ms</span>
                </div>
                <div class="trace-row">
                  <span class="lbl">github.searchCode</span>
                  <span class="track"
                    ><span class="bar" style="left:18%;width:34%"></span></span
                  >
                  <span class="dur">391ms</span>
                </div>
                <div class="trace-row">
                  <span class="lbl">linear.createIssue</span>
                  <span class="track"
                    ><span class="bar" style="left:52%;width:48%"></span></span
                  >
                  <span class="dur">612ms</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            {/* Teams */}
            <div class="cap-card">
              <span class="cap-icon"
                ><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                  ><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"
